  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is filed under the Minimal profile because the signature workflow has not yet completed; a sha256 content hash is present but no digital signature is attached. Pending signature workflow — W-SI-01 applies: structural integrity cannot be cryptographically verified until the ed25519 signature is appended by the authorising officer.",
